# Superpowers Cursor Integration

This project uses the Superpowers framework (located at `.skills/`) for systematic development.

Before performing any task or modifying any code:
1. Stop and brainstorm the design first. Refer to the `brainstorming` skill at `.skills/brainstorming/SKILL.md`.
2. Write a detailed implementation plan. Refer to the `writing-plans` skill at `.skills/writing-plans/SKILL.md`.
3. Follow Test-Driven Development (TDD) rules. Refer to the `test-driven-development` skill at `.skills/test-driven-development/SKILL.md`.
4. If debugging, follow the systematic debugging phases. Refer to the `systematic-debugging` skill at `.skills/systematic-debugging/SKILL.md`.

You must search and apply these skills from `.skills/` before replying.
